<h2 id="bayesian-bootstrap">Bayesian Bootstrap</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>purpose: estimate distribution for parameter</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Example:
(1) observed samples: array([ 3.34135494,  4.03678023,  0.4305536 ,  4.11717223]), which is actually from exponential(7)
(2) plot density
(3) need to simulation distribution of mean</p>
  </li>
</ul>

